headline.print_headline: FIFA Sponsor Expects Action Over Corruption Claims
headline.main: FIFA Sponsor Expects Action Over Corruption Claims

lead_paragraph: FIFA sponsor Anheuser-Busch says it is counting on football's ruling body to look into allegations of corruption that have been leveled over awarding the 2022 World Cup to Qatar.
